Package neureka.calculus

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Function
    Besides the Tsr class, which is the core class of Neureka, this interface and its implementations represents the second most important feature of this library.
    Function.CallOptions
    An API for calling a Function after having specified a set of Arg instances through the Function.callWith(Args) method.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FunctionCache
    This class is part of a given BackendContext instance responsible for caching Function references based on their String representation generated by Object.toString() as well as caching of results for active functions.
